{
  "stem": "4753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she called my parents the good [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lord, or not the God, but you now, I don't know an English expression for that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she loved them, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Klara.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she really had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things, you know, what other maids didn't have.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother have her every single year a month's paid vacation, what was unheard of in that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had freedom in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She did whatever she wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She could go out whenever she wanted, and so on, besides the work, what she knew what she was expected to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, 1939, when the Hitler era fell in Hungary, she wrote articles to newspapers about the unjust against the Jews, because she said how wonderful the Jewish people were to her.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was an orphan in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Jewish people raised her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our disappointment was unbelievable when the hardship came, and we had to go to the ghetto, that she didn't ever come to help us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after the war, when my other brother returned to Hungary, she-- he aslo took her in to the house, just to have vacation for her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did work for someone else that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and I was sending her packages from Sweden after the war, forgetting what she didn't do during the ghetto time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you took care of her after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, even she wasn't loyal to us, so to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she was-- he was drafted in 1941 in the Jewish Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what you are asking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once-- once he came home [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for three days.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
